{
  "chapter": 26,
  "chapter_summary": "浪莽山庄盟主大会上，\"神手\"战飞力推裴珏为江南绿林盟主，却遭\"金鸡\"向一啼暗中搅局。向一啼指使江湖宵小陈国良当众挑衅裴珏，欲令其当众出丑。不料裴珏挺身而出，一招便将陈国良击飞，展露出深不可测的武功，震惊四座。\"龙形八掌\"檀明趁势介入，以裴珏长辈身份当众认亲，令战飞精心策划的\"挟天子以令诸侯\"之计落空。向一啼见风使舵，转而全力支持裴珏为盟主。战飞虽满心不甘，却无法当众反悔，只得苦笑完成歃血大典。裴珏就此登上江南绿林盟主之位，檀明则借机重新拉拢裴珏，提及将女儿文琪许配于他，暗藏利用之心。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "向大哥今日此来，是以江南道上同源的身份参与此事的呢，抑或是——哼哼！\n兄弟我倒要向大哥给我一个明白。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "向一啼",
      "listener": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "text": "兄弟今日来此，只是来看看热闹的，难道不可以么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "今日我江南武林同道，歃血为盟，誓共生死，向兄亦是江南道上同源，却只是来看看热闹，嘿嘿！\n这却使兄弟我有些不懂了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "向一啼",
      "listener": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "text": "难道凡是江南武林同道，就全都要加盟此会的么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "众家兄弟，誓共生死，是友便非敌，是敌便非友，这其间绝无选择余地，是友是敌，但凭向兄一言而择，向兄若说今日此来只是看看热闹，说来便来，说去便去——哈哈，嘿嘿，哼哼！\n这却未免将这'浪莽山庄'看得太不值钱了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_guo_liang",
      "speaker_name": "陈国良",
      "listener": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "text": "是敌便非友，是友便非敌——哈哈，战庄主，难道江南武林中，不愿奉这'裴大先生'为盟主的人，便全都是敌而非友么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_chen_guo_liang",
      "text": "难道阁下还有什么异议不成？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_guo_liang",
      "speaker_name": "陈国良",
      "listener": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "text": "我们兄弟混饭吃，讲究的是白刀子进，红刀子出，枪尖上拼骨，刀头下舔血，纵然是刀山火海，枪林剑树，要你出出人人，你也不能有一丝一毫的含糊，战庄主，你说这话可是？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_chen_guo_liang",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_guo_liang",
      "speaker_name": "陈国良",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就是了，按说战庄主替我们选出的盟主，绝不会有什么差错，可是我陈国良不度德，不量力，却要来试试，这位裴大先生，是不是有惊人的艺业，超群的本事，能压得住我们这些刀头舔血的朋友。\n要是这位裴大先生的武功还不如我——哈哈！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_chen_guo_liang",
      "text": "你是谁？受了谁的指使，竟敢在这里撒野，这浪莽山庄，岂是你这下五门的狂徒撒野之地——来人呀！\n给我将这大胆狂徒抓出去。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "向一啼",
      "listener": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "怎地？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "向一啼",
      "listener": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "text": "这位陈兄弟说的话，一句也未曾说错，要想当江南武林盟主的人，不露个三招两式，嘿嘿——江南道上的数万个弟兄，怎能心服？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "这'裴大先生'乃兄弟我与莫氏兄弟、那大哥一起请来的，有谁不服的话，哼哼！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "向一啼",
      "listener": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "text": "如此说来，那不如让战兄你自做盟主好了，又何必——哼哼，做出这等局面来欺人耳目。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_guo_liang",
      "speaker_name": "陈国良",
      "listener": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "text": "是了，要是战庄主来做盟主，我陈四倒没有话说。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是极！\n是极。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_chen_guo_liang",
      "text": "你是准备要试一试我的武功么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "向一啼",
      "listener": "char_chen_guo_liang",
      "text": "不错，这位姓陈的朋友，正是找裴大……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_chen_guo_liang",
      "text": "你既然要找我较量武功，那么你就快些动手吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "向一啼",
      "listener": "char_chen_guo_liang",
      "text": "朋友既有心一试裴大先生的武功，此刻还不动手，更待何时？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "金鸡帮众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看他像是个汉子，哪知却是这样没种！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_guo_liang",
      "speaker_name": "陈国良",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "我与你拼了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抬下去……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "兄弟自问两眼不盲，各位对裴大先生的武功若是还有怀疑之处，不妨出来试试。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "珏儿，一年不见，想不到你武功居然精进如斯，真正令人可喜，我且敬你一杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "text": "大叔你这一向可好？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "还好，还好！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "text": "原来檀大侠竟是裴大先生素识……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "text": "珏儿自幼便和我住在一起，'素识'二字，似乎还不足以形容哩。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "珏儿，你说可是？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫只顾着自己欢喜，却忘了各位还有正事，珏儿，今日武林群豪此来，全是为着你一人而已，此后你做了江南绿林盟主，切切不可辜负了别人的雅爱，去去——快去照顾客人，唉！\n故人有后，真叫老夫高兴得很……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "text": "战庄主，方才歃血之誓，被那匹夫一扰，险些弄得不欢，所幸此刻已自无事，在座群豪，还有许多未曾饮得血酒，此刻还不赶快完成大典，老夫虽是局外人，却已等得有些心急了哩！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "text": "正是……正是……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "向一啼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "裴大先生不但少年英俊，想不到武功更是如此惊人，这种人来当江南盟主，我姓向的还有什么话说，来——兄弟们，且饮一杯血酒，贺我盟主之生！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "向一啼",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "自此以后，裴大先生就是我的盟主大哥，若有什么人对我大哥无礼，我姓向的第一个找他拼了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诸位可还有谁不曾饮过血酒？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位既是饮过血酒，便全是自己兄弟，但请随意吃喝，不要再客气了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "向一啼",
      "listener": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "text": "战庄主当真是众望所孚，登高一呼，江南武林中久未能决之事，于兹便告解决，我向一啼实在佩服得很，且敬战庄主一杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shou_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_jin_ji_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "我心里高兴极了……高兴极了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "唉！我知道你与琪儿青梅竹马，已经——但我们虽是武林中人，'礼教'二字，却也万万不可忘记，是以你那日在后花园中的情况，我极为不满，只是想不到你性情那般刚烈，竟然不告而别，我心里虽然生气，但见你走了，却还是担心的，你知不知道我曾叫过许多人出来找你？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "其实你只要好好做人，我便将琪儿许配于你，又有何不可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang_tan_ming",
      "text": "大叔，不知文琪妹子可还好么？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    }
  ],
